>>a9e2fd34-be22-4a2d-875f-fe09af31bce2
No video.

Don't understand why 08chan does not accept .mkv. It's a common format with technical excellence.

You lose something from transcoding, but can often bypass format wars by converting to webm. Webm is really just mkv - but using public codecs. Webm files play easily within any browser.

Quick and dirty way to convert is via ffmeg. Just put your file in a folder, then execute this on it: "ffmpeg -i *.mkv  1.webm" (ffmpeg doesn't like spaces)

 Finally, rename the webm file using the original title.

This is the only way currently available to generate up to date webm files.
